data.description: Enjoy the South Florida lifestyle.   This beautiful home was renovated in 2023 by NuConcept Properties.   From the moment you enter you'll feel like you're on vacation.   Styled in classic Bali Beach meets contemporary materials.   There isn't a detail overlooked.   New Kitchen, new bathrooms, new interior doors/trim and hardware, new 3rd bedroom/office with glass styled barn doors, new floors,  New Windows ( Sliders, kitchen, bedroom, front door) New appliances, New linen finish Custom Closets.    This house is comfort meets stylish.     The new owner will receive a 1 year  home warranty to include pool/pump/jets.   The excitement just continues as you step out to a new pool decking , lighting, service bar and all new landscaping.   Come visit and enjoy.
